OL,3,CRecycling plant that had eight fires
OL,4,Cthis year issues Christmas plea
OL,6,FITV News Meridian's Ciaran Fitzpatrick
OL,7,Fhas been to the re3 Recycling Centre,
OL,8,Fin Reading, to find out how the
OL,9,Findustry deals with a surge of festive
OL,10,Fscrap.
OL,12,FA recycling centre in Reading is
OL,13,Furging people to be mindful of how
OL,14,Fthey dispose of their rubbish this
OL,15,Ffestive season, as they expect a surge
OL,16,Fin waste over the coming weeks.
OL,18,FAround 3500 tonnes of recycling will
OL,19,Fbe arriving at the centre over the
OL,20,FChristmas fortnight.
