OL,4,Cthis year issues Christmas plea
OL,6,FAccording to the Environmental Agency,
OL,7,Fthe UK will generate 30% more waste
OL,8,Fover Christmas, and around three bags
OL,9,Fof waste on packaging alone.
OL,11,FHowever, with industry experts wanting
OL,12,Fthe country to move to a 'circular
OL,13,Feconomy,' wasting less and recycling
OL,14,Fmore, the centre worry that their
OL,15,Frubbish mountain may stack even higher.
OL,17,FA particular effort is being made to
OL,18,Fdispose of electronic goods in the
OL,19,Fproper way, as the Berkshire site has
OL,20,Ffaced 8 fires in 2024 alone.
