OL,3,CRecycling plant that had eight fires
OL,4,Cthis year issues Christmas plea
OL,6,FLaura Fisher, Contract Operations
OL,7,FManager at FCC Environment, considers
OL,8,Fher centre lucky for only having
OL,9,Feight, but she says that that is still
OL,10,Ftoo many.
OL,12,FShe said: "Four fires have had us to
OL,13,Fcall the fire and rescue service to
OL,14,Fsupport us in dealing with them so it
OL,15,Fis really important that people
OL,16,Fdispose of electronic items,
OL,17,Fespecially batteries and vapes, in the
OL,18,Fmost responsible way.
