OL,4,Cthis year issues Christmas plea
OL,6,F"That means do not put them in your
OL,7,Fbin at home, but instead put them in
OL,8,Fyour recycling or residual bin, or
OL,9,Fbring them to your local recycling
OL,10,Fcentre or supermarket.
OL,12,F"Disposable vapes are not a thing
OL,13,Funfortunately as it makes people think
OL,14,Fthat they can put them in any bin that
OL,15,Fthey can find whether that is your bin
OL,16,Fat home or a bin on the street.
OL,18,F"Unfortunately, that is not possible
OL,19,Fand will cause severe damage to our
OL,20,Ffacilities, dustcarts or even our
OL,21,Fpeople."
