OL,6,FAccording to industry statistics, 1 in
OL,7,F7 Brits buy more groceries than they
OL,8,Fneed over Christmas.
OL,10,FThe Berkshire-based site say that
OL,11,FChristmas dinners alone will count for
OL,12,Fnearly 1000 tonnes of their food waste
OL,13,Falone.
OL,15,FLaura Fisher said: "Food waste is a
OL,16,Freally important one. I don't think
OL,17,Fthat people understand how much we
OL,18,Foverbuy so much over Christmas and we
OL,19,Fthrow so much away.
